  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients undergoing thoracic surgery that require the placement of left-sided
             double-lumen tubes

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Preoperative hoarseness or sore throat

          -  History of upper airway diseases

          -  Anticipated difficult airway

          -  Anesthesia time longer than 6 hours
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
